Assign Cthangband: ""
CD Cthangband:

;*** Start Storage
Copy >NIL: Cthangband:Save/#?  Cthangband:Backup/ all
Delete >NIL: Cthangband:Save/#? all
CD Cthangband:backup
Echo >T:Cthangband_Character `requestfile title "Please select character to Store"` NOLINE
CD T:
Echo >Cthangband_CD "CD Cthangband:"
Echo >Cthangband_CopySource "Copy >NIL: backup/" NOLINE
Echo >Cthangband_CopyDest " storage/"
Echo >Cthangband_Delete "Delete >NIL: backup/" NOLINE
Join Cthangband_CD Cthangband_CopySource Cthangband_Character Cthangband_CopyDest Cthangband_Delete Cthangband_Character TO Cthangband_Script
Echo "" >>Cthangband_Script
Execute >NIL: Cthangband_Script
Delete >NIL: Cthangband_CD Cthangband_CopySource Cthangband_Character Cthangband_CopyDest Cthangband_Delete Cthangband_Script
;*** End Storage
